the higher the risk she would face.

202
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,960
Da Yin, remove it!

203
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:26,560
You can't remove it!

204
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,400
You can't remove the co-driver's door.

205
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:32,160
