227
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,680
Hurry up! Hurry up!

228
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,160
Hurry up!

229
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:18,720
Here.

230
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,440
Stay calm.

231
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,880
Liang! Get ready to remove it.

232
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,960
