270
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:28,080
Don't be afraid. I am here.

271
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,960
I am very afraid now.

272
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,920
Don't be afraid. I am here.

273
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:34,640
I will protect you.

274
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:36,170
