386
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:33,680
Nothing. Work on your thesis!

387
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,520
You busybody.

388
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:51,800
Sir!

389
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:52,760
Come in!

390
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:02,880
