539
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:24,160
Got it.

540
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:24,880
Go and check on Wu.

541
00:24:25,080 --> 00:24:26,840
Brother Wu, don't take it seriously.

542
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:29,840
He was good at conducting the operation.

543
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:31,240
