553
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,040
Two commanders

554
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,040
in a rescue operation.

555
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:59,400
One directed to extinguish the fire,

556
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:01,040
