562
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:14,360
This is our job.

563
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,200
Do you understand?

564
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:15,960
Yes!

565
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:18,240
Huo Yan.

566
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:19,560
Here!

567
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:21,520
